#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid "Calibrate Game Controller"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:37
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "This module provides an interface to calibrate your joystick device as "
#| "well as see which functions on your joystick are mapped to which logical "
#| "button or axis."
msgid ""
"This module provides an interface to calibrate your game controller as well "
"as see which functions on your game controller are mapped to which logical "
"button or axis."
msgstr ""
"See moodul võimaldab kalibreerida juhtkangiseadet ning näha, millised "
"juhtkangi funktsioonid on seotud milliste loogiliste nuppude või telgedega."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:43
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Here's a screenshot of the joystick module"
msgid "Here's a screenshot of the game controller module"
msgstr "Juhtlangi mooduli pilt"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid "The game controller module"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid "Device"
msgstr "Seade"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:58
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Here you can see the logical location of the device. If you have more "
#| "than one joystick device, you can also select which one to configure."
msgid ""
"Here you can see the logical location of the device. If you have more than "
"one game controller, you can also select which one to configure."
msgstr ""
"Siin näeb seadme loogilist asukohta. Kui sul on mitu juhtkangiseadet, saad "
"valida, millist seadistada."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:62
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If no joystick device is automatically found on your computer and you "
#| "know that there is one attached, you can enter the correct device file "
#| "here."
msgid ""
"If no game controller is automatically found on your computer and you know "
"that there is one attached, you can enter the correct device file here."
msgstr ""
"Kui arvutis ei leitud automaatselt ühtegi juhtpuldiseadet, aga sa tead, et "
"see on ühendatud, saab siis määrata korrektse seadmefaili."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid "Position"
msgstr "Positsioon"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:70
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The plotted location of the X and Y axes of the joystick. Enable "
#| "<guibutton>Show trace</guibutton> to plot the path of the joystick from "
#| "one point to another."
msgid ""
"The plotted location of the X and Y axes of the game controller's joystick. "
"Enable <guibutton>Show trace</guibutton> to plot the path of the joystick "
"from one point to another."
msgstr ""
"Juhtkangi X- ja Y-telje asukoht. Kui lülitada sisse <guibutton>Jälje "
"näitamine</guibutton>, joonistatakse juhtkangi teekond ühest punktist teise."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the joystick cannot reach every point on this graph, or if it does not "
"center correctly, you need to calibrate your device."
msgstr ""
"Kui juhtkang ei ulatu joonise igasse punkti või ei tsentreeri korrektselt, "
"tuleb seadet kalibreerida."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid "Buttons"
msgstr "Nupud"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:82
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "A place to see the pressed state of buttons on your joystick and if the "
#| "buttons are mapped correctly. When a joystick button is pressed, "
#| "<guilabel>PRESSED</guilabel> will appear next to the logical number (as "
#| "the computer sees it) of the button which was pressed."
msgid ""
"A place to see the pressed state of buttons on your game controller and if "
"the buttons are mapped correctly. When a button is pressed, "
"<guilabel>PRESSED</guilabel> will appear next to the logical number (as the "
"computer sees it) of the button which was pressed."
msgstr ""
"Siin näeb juhtkangi nuppude vajutatud olekut ning seda, kas nad on "
"korrektselt vastendatud. Juhtkangi nupu vajutamisel ilmub vajutatud nuüu "
"loogilise arvu (nagu seda näeb arvuti) kõrvale teade <guilabel>VAJUTATI</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid "Axes"
msgstr "Teljed"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:93
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "This displays the numerical values of the axis positions. 0 is centered "
#| "and the maximum and minimum values depend on the joystick and the "
#| "particular axis."
msgid ""
"This displays the numerical values of the axis positions. 0 is centered and "
"the maximum and minimum values depend on the game controller and the "
"particular axis."
msgstr ""
"See näitab teljepositsioonide arvväärtust. 0 on tsentreeritud, maksimum- ja "
"miinimumväärtused sõltuvad juhtkangist ja konkreetsest teljest."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid "Calibrate"
msgstr "Kalibreeri"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:102
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Clicking on <guibutton>Calibrate</guibutton> will open a dialog to "
#| "calibrate every axis on your joystick."
msgid ""
"Clicking on <guibutton>Calibrate</guibutton> will open a dialog to calibrate "
"every axis on your joysticks."
msgstr ""
"Klõps nupule <guibutton>Kalibreeri</guibutton> avab dialoogi, kus saab "
"kalibreerida juhtkangi kõiki telgi."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:108
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "<screeninfo>Calibrating your joystick</screeninfo>"
msgid "<screeninfo>Calibrating your game controller</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Juhtkangi kalibreerimine</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:114
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "<phrase>Calibrating your joystick</phrase>"
msgid "<phrase>Calibrating your game controller</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Juhtkangi kalibreerimine</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each axis will have to be moved to the minimum position, then the center, "
"and finally the maximum position. A meter in the bottom left corner of the "
"dialog will help determine which way increases and which way decreases the "
"values."
msgstr ""
"Iga telg liigutatakse miinimumpositsioon, siis tsentrisse ja lõpuks "
"maksimumpositsiooni. Dialoogis all vasakul asuv mõõdik aitab määrata, millal "
"väärtused suurenevad ja millal vähenevad."

